rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0010
rows.name:
We've collected a whole dragon's hoard of
genetic information.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0020
rows.name: Couldn't have done it without you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0030
rows.name: Thank you so much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0040
rows.name: I'm ready... I'll go back to NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0050
rows.name: Really?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0060
rows.name: Yes. See, while collecting the data, I heard voices.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0070
rows.name: The beings that made this world told me something:[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0080
rows.name: "To preserve...is to cultivate."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: xs32310100_SEL0010
rows.name: Intimate that you heard them too.

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0090
rows.name:
I didn't hear anything, personally...
But that sounds lovely.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_JNK0020
rows.name: Dismiss

rows.label: xs32310100_SEL0020
rows.name: Worry he might have inhaled hallucinogens.

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0100
rows.name: Not at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0110
rows.name: Ted here... He's listened to this world more than anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0120
rows.name: I'm not surprised it spoke to him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0130
rows.name: "To preserve is to cultivate," huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0140
rows.name: It's true that though this world will perish,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0145
rows.name: we can still plant its seeds...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0150
rows.name: in the next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0160
rows.name: Yes. I swear I'll make it happen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0170
rows.name: Whoa![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0180
rows.name: What's the deal?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0190
rows.name:
I'm afraid I may have trespassed on their territory
while I was collecting the data earlier...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0200
rows.name: We'll handle it. You just get to NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32310100_MSG0210
rows.name: As you say.[ST:wait ]
